Author: bubblyqueer
Text: I literally can’t do both residential and PHP. My leave from work would be too long and I wouldn’t get paid. Just tried to log in to my account for the hospital and it says my account is disabled. So guess I don’t get to know. I’m so scared to find out what they decide.

Author: kittypandaprincess
Text: I'm in the same boat, essentially. Waiting on labs in order to start treatment. I don't want to do residential, I'm scared, everything feels terrible... At least we're not alone?
